# Local drafts live here.
#
# Files in this folder are NOT parsed by lib/briefs.ts — the parser's
# readdirSync filter skips any top-level entry whose name starts with `_`.
#
# Workflow: `/api/draft/earnings` returns markdown. Drop it here as
# `YYYY-MM-DD-ticker-qN.md`, edit locally, then move the final file up to
# `content/briefings/` (remove the leading underscore / move out of _drafts/)
# before `git push`. Next deploy renders it, RSS picks it up, next morning's
# cron sends it.
